{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1603480/extras/TitleCard3.gif?t=1620508519\" /><br><br>Face down unfathomable evil in a unique roguelike experience with everything you can see at your disposal.<strong> If it exists in the world, you can throw it!</strong> Plates? Toss-able and deadly. Tables? Great for blocking a few extra hits and maybe a viable weapon! Barrels? Crates? Iron Maidens? All these items and more are strewn about this demonic dungeon. You will never be without a weapon so what's victory without a bit of greed, right?<br><br><strong>Fight Till the End and Conquer the Demon King!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1603480/extras/AvariceHeroArt_Smaller_.png?t=1620508519\" /><br><br>Will you survive the dungeon?<br>Or will you succumb to your own <strong>Avarice</strong>?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Chuck, hurl, and toss everything you can get your hands on!<br></li><li> Battle a variety of deadly enemies and watch them explode!<br></li><li> Experience procedurally generated levels (No two play-throughs will be the same!)<br></li><li> Explore an expansive dungeon with multiple levels. (at your own risk!)<br></li><li> Collect armor and weapons to defend yourself!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Powerful Weapons </strong></h2>Choose between three powerful weapons!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1603480/extras/2_way_promo.gif?t=1620508519\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Pierce Through Your Enemies With the Spear!</strong><br>Destroy multiple enemies with a strong throw of your trusty weapon.<br>Wind up and let it fly, but make sure it's fully charged, or else it might be hard to get it back.<br><br></li><li><strong> Smash Enemies to Bits With the Devastating Warhamm